dmca.title: DMCA notice to Google, Inc.
dmca.body:
September. 27, 2007 
FAX [private]
ATTN: blogger Legal Support, DMCA Complaints 
I am writing to inform you that one of your conk- -acted bloggers is running images in violation, of U.S. copyright laws. 
The images are four photographs of the actress Kate Walsh which were taken from the November 2007 issue of Marie Claire magazine and copyrighted by the Hearst Corporation.
